  "description": "A component that connects to GMI Cloud's large language models for advanced \nnatural language processing. GMI Cloud hosts 100+ OpenAI-compatible models \nincluding Llama 4, Qwen3, DeepSeek, GPT, Claude, and Gemini on owned H100/H200 \nGPU infrastructure. It enables capabilities like text generation, summarization, \nreasoning, and code understanding across a wide range of open-weight and \nproprietary models through a unified OpenAI-compatible API.",
  "documentation": "https://docs.rocketride.org",
  "icon": "gmi_cloud.svg",
  "lanes": {
    "questions": [
      "answers"
    ]
  },
